{"tid":1063011,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB重播《卡拉屋企》","createTime":"2019-03-15T12:47:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T03:21:11.000Z","uid":19889,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7520b82f89142aaeee588abc52fd3408b7a88f","tid":1063011,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2295000/2297261/53439382_1931823150260591_2318943754873298397_n_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2295000%2F2297261%2F53439382_1931823150260591_2318943754873298397_n_600.jpg&h=5ede20cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《如懿傳》大結局後，TVB深夜就開始會重播《卡拉屋企》，全劇一共有成227集，話晒依套劇都係唔少香港人嘅集體回憶，唔知TVB會唔會播足呢？「喂！夠鐘喇！睇電視！睇吓今集講乜先，講乜先？」淨係望到句字，已經全部回憶都返晒嚟呀！除咗首主題曲深入民心，劇情都非常吸引，最緊要係夠晒貼地。話時話，大家除咗相中嘅「白頭佬」、「肥媽」、「失魂菲」、「發記」、「泰臣」之外，仲記得幾多位演員？不過網友都好關心Popeye嘅近況，當年吳鎮宇帶同自己的愛犬一齊開工，而沙皮狗Popeye的表情楚楚可憐咁，吳鎮宇同埋劇中演員都好鍾意搓佢塊面，觀眾都覺得好得意，後來編劇特別加插Popeye的內心戲，由馮永和配音，令他們主僕情更加生動有趣。<br />\n<br />\n劇集距今已經28年，在吳鎮宇的社交平台都已經不再見到Popeye的影子，不過Popeye能夠拍到這部經典處境劇，絕對係吳鎮宇同Popeye之間最好的回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2295000/2297261/1470763728_329b_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2295000%2F2297261%2F1470763728_329b_600.jpg&h=728bb90c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3d4a5a9fde1e71c7a814d675b41f735de520bc1","tid":1063011,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:41:33.000Z","msg":"聽晚播 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679edb7da0860c884030427aee08c85f93fbf360","tid":1063011,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:43:04.000Z","msg":"香港地 要表態直言要上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd34d16c9e18aff0fd7a6b176ef516b1ce37217","tid":1063011,"uid":36877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:47:26.000Z","msg":"係真唔係真"},{"pid":"54f67f49e99ba6a8f9a564af1f9d20911084116a","tid":1063011,"uid":42848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:49:50.000Z","msg":"頭三十集太正路唔係咁好笑, 曾志偉客串嗰幾集開始啲劇情就開始痴撚線"},{"pid":"36cc3c1aa16abf085ce559c464c3a64000811e44","tid":1063011,"uid":56819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T17:56:36.000Z","msg":"又重播?不過點都好過播大陸劇"},{"pid":"80b5dbbaf596761352e06124aa8fb4f3cd9670f2","tid":1063011,"uid":57405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:19:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔報錯料？<br />\n《如懿傳》之後唔係播《法證先鋒》咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFAPFnG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFAPFnG.png&h=1ed824a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n《卡拉屋企》係接《皆大歡喜》"},{"pid":"a513494cff329dfa96b4e60b24d44b6e733db6b1","tid":1063011,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"之前又話播真情？"},{"pid":"cee1f5b853e4832a7bb808b9150f16797a096491","tid":1063011,"uid":58746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a513494cff329dfa96b4e60b24d44b6e733db6b1","tid":1063011,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"之前又話播真情？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"屌佢又黎?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a50822f06d51e4234bc938eb120789fd2789d3","tid":1063011,"uid":169457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a513494cff329dfa96b4e60b24d44b6e733db6b1","tid":1063011,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"之前又話播真情？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"真情係星期1-5, 朝早10:00做啊, 做左廿幾集啦"}]}